            <title>[HBASE-12613] [shell] Add online load of configuration changes for Master</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-12613</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Master accepts online load of configuration changes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This JIRA adds shell support for this feature such that user doesn&apos;t need to look up Master servername.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
